c: 13
v: 3
t: "Ni na we warambuye isi maze ayishyiraho imisozi n’imigezi. Yanashyize muri buri bwoko bw’imbuto amoko abiri abiri (iz’ibara ryera n’izirabura, inini n’into, iziryohera n’izirura), atwikiriza ijoro amanywa (amanywa na yo akayatwikiriza ijoro). Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo harimo ibimenyetso ku bantu batekereza"